  $}

  ${
    $d n x y J $.  $d n x y P $.  $d x y X $.
    sncld.1 $e |- X = U. J $.
    $( A singleton is closed in a Hausdorff space. $)
    sncld $p |- ( ( J e. Haus /\ P e. X ) -> { P } e. ( Clsd ` J ) ) $=
      ( vx vy vn cha wcel wa csn ccld cfv ccl wceq cv cin c0 wne wi wral ctop
